### Create Store
POST http://localhost:5002/store-api/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
   "name":"ABC Pharmacy",
   "category":"pharmacy",
   "address":"Hyderabad",
   "location":{
      "lat":17.385,
      "lng":78.486
   }
}

### Get Stores
GET http://localhost:5002/store-api/all

